snippet.title: IMPETUM - New Photorealistic Horror Game Trailer
snippet.description:
IMPETUM - new photorealistic first person horror game.

Impetum is a scary psychological horror. Upon returning home, the protagonist realizes that something wrong is going on in the house and he has to deal with what is going on.

The game carries jump scares, scary moments, puzzle.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3137930/IMPETUM/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/truegamesstudio/
Twitter: https://x.com/TrueGamesStudio
